        "TileImage": "$($repository 25d7b1c0-873e-4b7a-ac40-5502b88eedc9).Image",
        "Description": "Disgruntled Employees Receive Inside Information About A Multi-Million-Dollar Play In the Stock Market From The CFO Of A Large Hege Fund. They Are Planning To Stage A Coup Within The Bank, And Want To Take The Opposite Side Of The Trade Using The Hedge Funds Reserves, Then Wiring The Profits To Multiple Off-Shore Accounts That Cannot Be Traced. Unfortunately, This  Hedge Fund Contributes To Our Organization, And Is A Valuable Asset. Eliminate The Targets Before Their Plan Becomes Succesful.",
